OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773399918
OL,3,CThe power of payback
OL,5,FOne of the things that has been a
OL,6,Fconsistent theme since we started the
OL,7,FGoing the Extra Mile podcast has been
OL,8,Fthe power of giving back.
OL,10,FRegardless of background, age or
OL,11,Fgender, those who have been supported
OL,12,Fthrough a low point in their life
OL,13,Funderstand the power of help, of
OL,14,Fkindness and know that with the tools
OL,15,Fto succeed, lives can be turned round.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773399918
OL,3,CThe power of payback
OL,5,FLinda and Patrick are my guests this
OL,6,Fweek. Two young people who have faced
OL,7,Fserious challenges in their lives,
OL,8,Fthey were supported by the Kings Trust
OL,9,Fto change the trajectory of their
OL,10,Flives and now they embody the concept
OL,11,Fof giving back.
OL,13,FLinda is a refugee from Central
OL,14,FAmerica. Originally a teacher,
OL,15,Fadjusting to life in Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fwhilst not allowed to work severely
OL,17,Ftested her mental health. By the time
OL,18,Fshe found the Kings Trust, she felt
OL,19,Finvisible in this new society.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773399918
OL,3,CThe power of payback
OL,5,F'They opened to make me feel
OL,6,Fempowered. When I joined the courses,
OL,7,Fevery time I was going, I was feeling
OL,8,Fmore alive, more happy, and I was
OL,9,Ffeeling more confident. Their job is
OL,10,Fgiving you all the confidence and I
OL,11,Fdon't know where they found it, so it
OL,12,Fwas a real help for me," she said.
OL,14,F"And then, thank God they saw me a
OL,15,Flittle bit more than the other
OL,16,Forganisations. As a refugee, I was
OL,17,Fasking for mental health and I didn't
OL,18,Fget it. And I was getting very, very
OL,19,Fdown.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773399918
OL,3,CThe power of payback
OL,5,F"One of the girls on the King's Trust,
OL,6,Fthey saw that I was not that bubbly
OL,7,Fpersonality as normal. And I expressed
OL,8,Fto them that I needed help. I was
OL,9,Freally having difficulties to keep
OL,10,Fbeing alive. And they helped me by
OL,11,Fgiving a therapist for six weeks."
OL,13,FLinda said the therapist was able to
OL,14,Fhelp her identify little issues she
OL,15,Fhad not realised before.
OL,17,F"The therapist has been my saviour."
OL,19,F"Between that and the courses, I was
OL,20,Ffeeling even another Linda that I
OL,21,Fnever knew I was able to be."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773399918
OL,3,CThe power of payback
OL,5,FPatrick had a difficult time as a
OL,6,Fteenager. In trouble with the law,
OL,7,Fskipping school, He admits he was
OL,8,Fgoing down the wrong path, a path
OL,9,Fwhich wasn't a reflection of the
OL,10,Fperson he truly is.
OL,12,F"Before I got the support, I had very
OL,13,Flow, low mental health. There were a
OL,14,Flot of issues surrounding substance
OL,15,Fmisuse and anger and just a lot of
OL,16,Fteenage stuff as well amongst trauma
OL,17,Fand stuff from the past.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773399918
OL,3,CThe power of payback
OL,5,F"So the support that was able to put
OL,6,Fin place, it helped me break down
OL,7,Fthose barriers and kind of find
OL,8,Fmyself, break the cycle and be able to
OL,9,Fcome out as a different person with a
OL,10,Fbetter outlook on life. It helped
OL,11,Fmassively with the moods and with
OL,12,Fconnecting with other people as well."
OL,14,FBoth Linda and Patrick recognise that
OL,15,Fthe support they received changed
OL,16,Ftheir lives and that gave them the
OL,17,Frealisation that they have the power
OL,18,Fwithin themselves to change the lives
OL,19,Fof others.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773399918
OL,3,CThe power of payback
OL,5,FLinda is now an Ambassador for the
OL,6,FKings Trust, a role that she relishes.
OL,8,F"My experience can sell it more than
OL,9,Fmy words. Being in that lower, lower
OL,10,Fposition at that moment and now
OL,11,Ffeeling so good about it.
OL,13,F"With the young ambassador position,
OL,14,Fbeing able to speak out about women's
OL,15,Frights, about mental health, about in
OL,16,Fmy case personally, about refugees and
OL,17,Fasylum seekers. And having the
OL,18,Fopportunity to share that has been the
OL,19,Fbest way that I have at the moment to
OL,20,Fgive out all the help that they gave
OL,21,Fto me."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773399918
OL,3,CThe power of payback
OL,5,FListening to Patrick who now studies
OL,6,Fat university and who mentors other
OL,7,Fyoung people, you can almost hear the
OL,8,Fpride in his voice when he describes
OL,9,Fhis life now.
OL,11,F"For me, growing up as I mentioned,
OL,12,Fbeing in care,, as well as having a
OL,13,Flot of negative experiences for a long
OL,14,Ftime, it felt that people weren't
OL,15,Fgiving enough to me. Giving me the
OL,16,Fhelp to help me grow and to flourish
OL,17,Fand to see my potential.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773399918
OL,3,CThe power of payback
OL,5,F"So for me, the importance of giving
OL,6,Fback, me wanting to give back, is that
OL,7,Fno other young person has to feel the
OL,8,Fway that I felt, when I felt nobody
OL,9,Fwas giving enough to me. That there is
OL,10,Fsomeone there who wants to see them
OL,11,Fgrow, who wants to see their potential
OL,12,Fand who's willing to give their time
OL,13,Fand to give their care and dedication
OL,14,Fto that young person to see them
OL,15,Fbecome who they can truly be.
OL,17,F"So I feel like giving back is one of
OL,18,Fthe most important things that we
OL,19,Fcould do, not just through our job,
OL,20,Fbut I feel as a society as well, to
OL,21,Fhelp other people around us."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
